name: Ahmed Khalifa
note:
Ahmed Khalifa:
Hi Christina,
It's great connecting with you. Could you please tell me more about Remote Helpers, what services you provide, and how we might cooperate?

Christina Heil:
Hello Ahmed! Thanks for adding me! I represent Remote Helpers, an outstaffing company.
Our candidates can fill various positions, such as Developers, Lead Generation Managers, Customer Support, Personal Assistants, Social Media Managers, Designers, Media Buyers, PPC, SEO, AdOps, and English teachers, among others.
We have available candidates with video CVs, ready to discuss how we could meet your needs. Would you be interested in a call to explore this further?
Warm Regards,
Christina, Remote Helpers

Ahmed Khalifa:
Thank you for sharing the details.
I’m the Director of Sales at HealthCare Incorporation in Doha, Qatar, and I also represent Simulead in Dubai, UAE. What are the nationalities of your candidates?

Christina Heil:
Thank you for the information.
We are a multinational team, but most of our candidates are Ukrainians who speak English and often other languages as well. Could this pose any issues?

Ahmed Khalifa:
No issues with Ukrainian nationals in Qatar. We face visa challenges with some nationalities, but Ukrainians are fine.
Do you have candidates with a biomedical engineering background who could work in sales for biomedical equipment or healthcare education simulators?

Christina Heil:
We may not have candidates specifically in biomedical engineering, but we do have those with a technical background and sales experience.
Please note that our candidates work remotely.

Ahmed Khalifa:
Technical background would be acceptable, though we prefer on-site in Qatar. I’ll reach out if we need remote support. Thanks for all the information.

Christina Heil:
Thank you, Ahmed. Please keep us in mind, and feel free to reach out when needed. Here’s our website: rh-s.com (it might require a VPN in Qatar).
Best Regards,
Christina, Remote Helpers

Ahmed Khalifa:
Sure, Christina. I’ll look at your website and let you know when we have requirements, especially with plans to expand in 2025. We also work with Russian-speaking suppliers, which could align well with your candidates’ language skills.
We also have suppliers from Japan, Germany, Austria, and Miami, and provide training for our teams worldwide. Here’s our main U.S. supplier: Gaumard.

Christina Heil:
You’re right, many of our candidates are fluent in Russian and English.
We also have an affiliate program where partners help attract clients and earn a profit. Would you be interested in discussing this further?

Ahmed Khalifa:
Yes, I believe in the skills of Eastern European professionals. I’ve been to Ukraine and Russia and know their capabilities well.

Christina Heil:
We appreciate the positive feedback. Our team is known for professionalism and high-quality work. If you’re interested, we’d be happy to discuss more details on a call.

Ahmed Khalifa:
Спасибо большое. Let’s arrange a call next week. I’ll follow up with details.

Christina Heil:
Hi Ahmed,
Have you thought more about our offer? Do you have time this or next week to discuss potential cooperation? We’re eager to connect.

Ahmed Khalifa:
Hello Christina, sure. Let’s arrange a call on Thursday. I’ll confirm the time tomorrow.

Christina Heil:
Looking forward to your confirmation. Have a great day!

Ahmed Khalifa:
Thanks, you too. I’ll let you know about our availability tomorrow morning.

Ahmed Khalifa:
Sorry for the late reply, Christina. I should be available Monday between 11:00 AM and 1:00 PM Doha time. Will that work for you?

Christina Heil:
No worries, Ahmed! We work with busy people and understand. Looking forward to cooperating.

Ahmed Khalifa:
Thank you. I’ve been occupied today. Monday would be better for a call. Let’s arrange it for then.

Christina Heil:
Sure, let’s set it for Monday. Could you give me a tentative time?

Ahmed Khalifa:
Let’s schedule it for Monday at 1:00 PM Doha time. Does that work?

Christina Heil:
There’s another call scheduled at 1:00 PM. Would 1:30 PM work instead?

Ahmed Khalifa:
Yes, 1:30 PM onwards is fine.

Christina Heil:
Please share your email so I can send the Google Meet link.

Ahmed Khalifa:
A.khalifa@healthcareinc.org
